{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-component-tsx","path":"/component/Form/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"e408476f-2c52-5cc3-9acf-cef1f01b319b","excerpt":"简介 表单  是信息添加、录入的通用形式，是用户输入的重要交互方式。 表单  作为其他组件（单选 、 数字输入框 、 输入框 等等）的容器的同时，还为其他组件提供布局的功能。 U-Design 的表单  只负责布局和展示，不提供任何逻辑功能和表单校验。 基本构成  标题（A） 配置项标题（B） 输入域（C…","html":"<!--副标题具体写法见源代码模式-->\n<h2 id=\"简介\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E7%AE%80%E4%BB%8B\" aria-label=\"简介 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>简介</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>表单 <code class=\"language-text\">Form</code> 是信息添加、录入的通用形式，是用户输入的重要交互方式。</li>\n<li>表单 <code class=\"language-text\">Form</code> 作为其他组件（单选 <code class=\"language-text\">Radio</code>、 数字输入框 <code class=\"language-text\">NumberInput</code>、 输入框 <code class=\"language-text\">Input</code>等等）的容器的同时，还为其他组件提供布局的功能。</li>\n<li>U-Design 的表单 <code class=\"language-text\">Form</code> 只负责布局和展示，不提供任何逻辑功能和表单校验。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"基本构成\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%9E%84%E6%88%90\" aria-label=\"基本构成 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>基本构成</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1440px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 48.33333333333333%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"forms 01\"\n        title=\"forms 01\"\n        src=\"/u-design/static/56ad2ddc9130ab48341e587480c8b5a3/07a9c/forms_01.png\"\n        srcset=\"/u-design/static/56ad2ddc9130ab48341e587480c8b5a3/f21e7/forms_01.png 360w,\n/u-design/static/56ad2ddc9130ab48341e587480c8b5a3/37523/forms_01.png 720w,\n/u-design/static/56ad2ddc9130ab48341e587480c8b5a3/07a9c/forms_01.png 1440w,\n/u-design/static/56ad2ddc9130ab48341e587480c8b5a3/e8950/forms_01.png 2000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"center\">标题（A）</th>\n<th align=\"center\">配置项标题（B）</th>\n<th align=\"center\">输入域（C）</th>\n<th align=\"center\">提示信息（D）</th>\n<th align=\"center\">说明信息（E）</th>\n<th align=\"center\">必选项标识（F）</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">√</td>\n<td align=\"center\">√</td>\n<td align=\"center\">√</td>\n<td align=\"center\">√</td>\n<td align=\"center\">可选</td>\n<td align=\"center\">可选</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><strong>A.标题</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>帮助对信息进行分组，方便用户填写</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>B.配置项标题</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>主要是解释输入项的含义，一般不宜太长，需要简明扼要，快速让用户理解</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>B.输入域</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>可交互输入的区域，是构成表单的核心内容，用来收集用户操作的信息；</li>\n<li>作为容器主要放置：单选 <code class=\"language-text\">Radio</code>、 数字输入框 <code class=\"language-text\">NumberInput</code>、 输入框 <code class=\"language-text\">Input</code>等组件</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>C.提示信息</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>包含帮助信息、占位符和反馈信息提示</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>D.说明信息（可选）</strong></p>\n<!--交互补充交互补充交互补充交互补充交互补充交互补充交互补充-->\n<p><strong>E.必选标识（可选）</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>告知用户当前项为必填项，不可为空值</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"基本样式\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%A0%B7%E5%BC%8F\" aria-label=\"基本样式 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>基本样式</h2>\n<h3 id=\"尺寸\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%B0%BA%E5%AF%B8\" aria-label=\"尺寸 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>尺寸</h3>\n<p>表单 <code class=\"language-text\">Form</code> 预设了 <code class=\"language-text\">md</code>、<code class=\"language-text\">lg</code>两种尺寸，高度分别为28px、32px。</p>\n<p>中号表单</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1440px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 40.27777777777778%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"styles 01\"\n        title=\"styles 01\"\n        src=\"/u-design/static/131191c2acd811d3fca710ea07b3734f/07a9c/styles_01.png\"\n        srcset=\"/u-design/static/131191c2acd811d3fca710ea07b3734f/f21e7/styles_01.png 360w,\n/u-design/static/131191c2acd811d3fca710ea07b3734f/37523/styles_01.png 720w,\n/u-design/static/131191c2acd811d3fca710ea07b3734f/07a9c/styles_01.png 1440w,\n/u-design/static/131191c2acd811d3fca710ea07b3734f/e8950/styles_01.png 2000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>大号表单</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1440px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 40.27777777777778%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"styles 02\"\n        title=\"styles 02\"\n        src=\"/u-design/static/594e6a6be44daefcd7c0b8e399eae596/07a9c/styles_02.png\"\n        srcset=\"/u-design/static/594e6a6be44daefcd7c0b8e399eae596/f21e7/styles_02.png 360w,\n/u-design/static/594e6a6be44daefcd7c0b8e399eae596/37523/styles_02.png 720w,\n/u-design/static/594e6a6be44daefcd7c0b8e399eae596/07a9c/styles_02.png 1440w,\n/u-design/static/594e6a6be44daefcd7c0b8e399eae596/e8950/styles_02.png 2000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"布局\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80\" aria-label=\"布局 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>布局</h3>\n<p>表单中的标签放置理论具体可以参考 <a href=\"https://www.uxmatters.com/mt/archives/2006/07/label-placement-in-forms.php\">这篇文章</a> ，U-Design 目前提供了以下两种布局形式：</p>\n<h4 id=\"横向对齐\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%A8%AA%E5%90%91%E5%AF%B9%E9%BD%90\" aria-label=\"横向对齐 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>横向对齐</h4>\n<p>优点：文字开头按阅读视线对齐，符合人们的阅读习惯，节约纵向空间。</p>\n<p>缺点：填写速度慢，标签长度和输入框弹性小。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1440px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 36.66666666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"styles 03\"\n        title=\"styles 03\"\n        src=\"/u-design/static/c1ef45c572a261f986fca708d2316d1f/07a9c/styles_03.png\"\n        srcset=\"/u-design/static/c1ef45c572a261f986fca708d2316d1f/f21e7/styles_03.png 360w,\n/u-design/static/c1ef45c572a261f986fca708d2316d1f/37523/styles_03.png 720w,\n/u-design/static/c1ef45c572a261f986fca708d2316d1f/07a9c/styles_03.png 1440w,\n/u-design/static/c1ef45c572a261f986fca708d2316d1f/e8950/styles_03.png 2000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h4 id=\"纵向对齐\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E7%BA%B5%E5%90%91%E5%AF%B9%E9%BD%90\" aria-label=\"纵向对齐 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>纵向对齐</h4>\n<p>优点：采用顶部对齐的标签样式，浏览表单所需的时间最短；同时标签长度弹性大。</p>\n<p>缺点：非常占纵向空间。<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1440px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 48.611111111111114%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=