argin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1440px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 35.27777777777778%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"styles 06\"\n        title=\"styles 06\"\n        src=\"/u-design/static/73907ff9b7b1582c205fecf0e9f5c2e3/07a9c/styles_06.png\"\n        srcset=\"/u-design/static/73907ff9b7b1582c205fecf0e9f5c2e3/f21e7/styles_06.png 360w,\n/u-design/static/73907ff9b7b1582c205fecf0e9f5c2e3/37523/styles_06.png 720w,\n/u-design/static/73907ff9b7b1582c205fecf0e9f5c2e3/07a9c/styles_06.png 1440w,\n/u-design/static/73907ff9b7b1582c205fecf0e9f5c2e3/e8950/styles_06.png 2000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"基本状态\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E7%8A%B6%E6%80%81\" aria-label=\"基本状态 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>基本状态</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1440px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 17.22222222222222%; posit