=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>帮助信息</h3>\n<p>有些场景下需要帮助性信息，来辅助用户完成表单填写。当帮助信息的重要级比较高时，可以直接放在改输入框的附近。如果帮助信息的重要级比较低，则可以通过 文字提示 <code class=\"language-text\">Tooltip</code> 组件来实现，获取鼠标焦点的时候，则展开信息，失去焦点则消失（在气泡展开时，切忌勿挡住input输入框）。</p>\n<p>如果是针对全局的帮助性信息，可以放在表单的顶部；</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1440px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 40.833333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"descriptions 01\"\n        title=\"descriptions 01\"\n        src=\"/u-design/static/ba2a88e3bd621055318f2fa3fa6ccfb5/07a9c/descriptions_01.png\"\n        srcset=\"/u-design/static/ba2a88e3bd621055318f2fa3fa6ccfb5/f21e7/descriptions_01.png 360w,\n/u-design/static/ba2a88e3bd621055318f2fa3fa6ccfb5/37523/descriptions_01.png 720w,\n/u-design/static/ba2a88e3bd621055318f2fa3fa6ccfb5/07a9c/descriptions_01.png 1440w,\n/u-design/static/ba2a88e3bd621055318f2fa3fa6ccfb5/e8950/descriptions_01.png 2000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>如果只是针对某个元素提醒，则应将两者放在一起，让用户知道当前处于什么地方，在针对什么进行引导、辅助。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1440px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 40.833333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"descriptions 02\"\n        title=\"descriptions 02\"\n        src=\"/u-design/static/b3104badfda1ddb028463876e43c6a96/07a9c/descriptions_02.png\"\n        srcset=\"/u-design/static/b3104badfda1ddb028463876e43c6a96/f21e7/descriptions_02.png 360w,\n/u-design/static/b3104badfda1ddb028463876e43c6a96/37523/descriptions_02.png 720w,\n/u-design/static/b3104badfda1ddb028463876e43c6a96/07a9c/descriptions_02.png 1440w,\n/u-design/static/b3104badfda1ddb028463876e43c6a96/e8950/descriptions_02.png 2000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"反馈提示\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%8F%8D%E9%A6%88%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA\" aria-label=\"反馈提示 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>反馈提示</h3>\n<p>包括实时 (操作中) 校验用户录入数据的合规性，和告知用户操作后的结果状态两种。U-Design 的 表单 <code class=\"language-text\">Form</code> 只负责提供反馈样式，不提供任何逻辑功能和表单校验。</p>\n<h3 id=\"分模块\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%88%86%E6%A8%A1%E5%9D%97\" aria-label=\"分模块 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>分模块</h3>\n<p>化繁为简是人处理复杂事物常用的方法，如果需要一次性输入、提交大量数据，我们为了提高用户填写效率，减少用户心理负担，可将填写内容进行分模块，用户可以在填写好一段内容后进行心理上停顿休息，减少视觉疲劳和心理压力。\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1440px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 64.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"descriptions 03\"\n        title=\"descriptions 03\"\n        src=\"/u-design/static/e7a34065cabbba66cd6a182ca8a43adf/07a9c/descriptions_03.png\"\n        srcset=\"/u-design/static/e7a34065cabbba66cd6a182ca8a43adf/f21e7/descriptions_03.png 360w,\n/u-design/static/e7a34065cabbba66cd6a182ca8a43adf/37523/descriptions_03.png 720w,\n/u-design/static/e7a34065cabbba66cd6a182ca8a43adf/07a9c/descriptions_03.png 1440w,\n/u-design/static/e7a34065cabbba66cd6a182ca8a43adf/e8950/descriptions_03.png 2000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"高级选项默认收起，点击展开\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E9%AB%98%E7%BA%A7%E9%80%89%E9%A1%B9%E9%BB%98%E8%AE%A4%E6%94%B6%E8%B5%B7%EF%BC%8C%E7%82%B9%E5%87%BB%E5%B1%95%E5